  "body": "**Is your feature request related to a problem? Please describe.**\r\nAfter #2073, lodestar explicitly uses `phase0` types everywhere.\r\nThere's an exercise that needs to be done to make lodestar HF-ready.\r\nIMO should wait until we've merged the `lightclient` branch into master and actually have multiple versions of types.\r\n\r\n**Describe the solution you'd like**\r\nWherever multiple versions of an object may be in use, use `config.getTypes` instead of `config.types.phase0`.\r\n\r\neg: in API, returning a `BeaconState` (in the debug API), wherever it said `config.types.phase0.BeaconState.toJson(state)`, replace that with `config.getTypes(state.slot).BeaconState.toJson(state)` (This may require the return types of the API to also change)\r\n\r\n",
